data.description: LISTED BELOW APPRAISAL VAULE!!!  Welcome to your dream home in the heart of South Austin! This nicely updated one-story gem is nestled on a huge corner lot in the sought-after Cherry Creek neighborhood, offering both modern comfort and convenient city living. Just moments away from downtown, this location is a true urban paradise. Step inside and be amazed by the tasteful upgrades that define every corner of this home. The kitchen is a culinary enthusiast's delight, boasting recently replaced cabinetry, elegant granite countertops, a stylish backsplash that adds a pop of personality, stainless steel appliances, and convenient open shelving. Large master bedroom with plenty of closet space and the attached master bathroom boasts a generously sized walk-in shower that transforms your daily routine into a spa-like experience. Beautiful laminate hardwood flooring flows seamlessly throughout the home. Stay cool with the new HVAC while natural light dances through the low-e double-pane windows, casting a warm glow that welcomes you at every turn. Brand new rain gutters and recently replaced siding not only enhances the curb appeal but also adds to the home's overall energy efficiency. Brand new fencing gives privacy to an expansive backyard and is a canvas for your outdoor dreams, offering ample space for gardening, play, or relaxation. But the true highlight is the charming treehouse, complete with a slide that promises hours of endless fun for the young and young at heart. This is more than just a home; it's an opportunity to immerse yourself in Austin's vibrant culture while enjoying the tranquility of a well-loved neighborhood. Don't miss out on this chance to make cherished memories in a house that seamlessly blends style, comfort, and convenience. Your Austin dream starts right here!
